"Inverse hyperbolic sine transfer: linear below the softening knee k, "
"logarithmic above.\n"
"Adjust k in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Invers hyperbolsk sinus-overføring: lineær under mykneknekken k, logaritmisk "
"over.\n"
"Juster k i animasjonsdialogen."

#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10997
